(2167, 1, '2018-10-31 13:30:26', '2018-10-31 13:30:26', 'On the eve of D-Day, American paratroopers drop behind enemy lines to penetrate the walls of a fortified church and destroy a radio transmitter. As the soldiers approach their target, they soon begin to realize that there\'s more going on in the Nazi-occupied village than a simple military operation.<span class=\"yZlgBd\"> Making their way to an underground lab, the outnumbered men stumble upon a sinister experiment that forces them into a vicious battle against an army of the undead.</span>', 'Overlord', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'overlord', '', '', '2018-10-31 14:39:37', '2018-10-31 14:39:37', '', 0, 'http://localhost/unite/?post_type=films&#038;p=2167', 0, 'films', '', 0),
