(2169, 1, '2018-10-31 13:32:41', '2018-10-31 13:32:41', 'Hundreds of years after civilization was destroyed by a cataclysmic event, a mysterious young woman, Hester Shaw (Hera Hilmar), emerges as the only one who can stop London — now a giant, predator city on wheels — from devouring everything in its path. Feral, and fiercely driven by the memory of her <span class=\"yZlgBd\">mother, Hester joins forces with Tom Natsworthy (Robert Sheehan), an outcast from London, along with Anna Fang (Jihae), a dangerous outlaw with a bounty on her head.</span>', 'Mortal Engines', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'mortal-engines', '', '', '2018-10-31 15:56:08', '2018-10-31 15:56:08', '', 0, 'http://localhost/unite/?post_type=films&#038;p=2169', 0, 'films', '', 0),
